summary: This mod is a mod that allows you to equip Wings on your character!!
descriptionHtml:
DESCRIPTION: 

This mod is a mod that allows you to add Wings onto your character I did review this mod in my video and if you could watch that, that would be awesome my name is KILLZAMOI please SUBSCRIBE!! 

The Video: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E3ITNvG6nH8

INSTALLATION:

This mod is very easy to install either install it with nexus mod manager. Then go into your game and to get this mod you have to actually use command codes the button is this (~`) and then you want to write (help wings) without brackets and all these wings you can get should pop up and it should say something like this for one of them. Watch my video on what to do here its to hard to explain in words.
